Subject: [PATCH 29/35] ci: add opt-in real-engines workflow with preflight
 gate

workflow_dispatch + weekly cron; preflight-gated graceful skip; no
LLM/API keys; env overrides LEV_JULIA_BIN + LEV_PY; runs the
unstubbed real-evidence loop tests. Locally dry-run verified.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
